{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">   <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202400/extras/Start2.gif?t=1736978423\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Physics-Based Fun:</strong> Experience the thrill of realistic physics with a fun twist.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    <strong>Competition and Strategy:</strong> A perfect mix of luck and skill-based gameplay.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    <strong>Variety and Excitement:</strong> From challenging single-player levels to entertaining multiplayer modes, there\u2019s something for everyone!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Join the world of Ball Race Party now! The finish line awaits you!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Single Player Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Race against the clock! In this mode, you\u2019ll face increasingly difficult tracks that test your speed and skills. Complete levels in the fastest time possible to claim the top spot on the global leaderboard. Think fast, act smart, and break records!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202400/extras/single.gif?t=1736978423\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Multiplayer Modes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ball Race Party</strong> offers two exciting multiplayer modes:</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>1. Multiplayer Challenge Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Time to showcase your skills! In this mode, you race against other players to complete a challenging track as fast as possible. Overcome obstacles, act strategically, and leave your opponents behind. Remember, it's not just about speed but also tactics!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>2. Multiplayer Lucky Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Out of your control! The ball you choose moves entirely on its own while you watch in anticipation. Trust your luck and hope your ball crosses the finish line before your rivals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202400/extras/lucky.gif?t=1736978423\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Special Abilities</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use these fun abilities during the race to hinder your rivals and gain an advantage:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fart</strong>: Create a temporary barrier to block opponents coming from behind. Timing is everything!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bomb</strong>: Knock your rivals off the track with an explosive blast. Use it strategically to seize the lead.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"TOY DUCK","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3202400/32c365dddc333e7548e741bb669d0c6cddf038c8.jpg"},{"name":"TOY BALLOON","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3202400/8396f94459d145ee08017adc4dffbe6c321fcd6f.jpg"},{"name":"TOY SOLDIER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3202400/40c9ad643c0fa22f6333716b2c62a14bf5b50229.jpg"},{"name":"TOY CAR","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3202400/101518654af41ab564863dee1368b2faf83de7b1.jpg"},{"name":"BOWLING PINS","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3202400/e8e3381a1b854553ef8f5a706265e57fdc3f2238.jpg"},{"name":"TEDDY BEAR","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3202400/15012d4bec53aa232d64d73c66f8c16a685e857f.jpg"},{"name":"TRAFFIC CONES","path":"https://cdn.akamai.ste